piskorski.obscure.fsm

Class FSM

  • java.lang.Object
    • piskorski.obscure.fsm.FSM
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class FSM
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class allows for using optimized finite-state machines which have been previously generated by the DFKI FSM Toolkit in C++ format. Finite-state machine is a generalization of weighted finite-state automata and weighted finite-state transducers. Once an FSM object is initialized from C++ format (*.fsm file)it can be saved in JAVA binary format for further use (which is highly recomended in order to achieve better efficiency).
